modShortDescription: This mod increases to 90 slots the storage boxes (secure storage chest and generic box) and greenDrawer.
modDescription:
This mod increases to 90 [slots](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-more-slots/) the storage boxes (secure storage chest and generic box) and greenDrawer.

Becaused TFP reduced the storage size of the secure storage chest, generic box and greenDrawer left them the same at 72 slots.

**[Download](http://www.mediafire.com/file/c91zcieq5ml1ic9/GK_Storage.rar/file)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/20168-gouki%C2%B4s-a19-modlets/).
